OL,3,CSeveral people treated following
OL,4,Cchemical spill at Guy's Hospital
OL,6,FA chemical spill at a major London
OL,7,Fhospital has left one person injured,
OL,8,Fwith several more treated for the
OL,9,Finhalation of chlorine gas.
OL,11,FFour of the nine patients were taken
OL,12,Fto hospital by ambulance crews
OL,13,Ffollowing the incident, which took
OL,14,Fplace in a non-patient area of Guy's
OL,15,FHospital in Southwark.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the hospital urged
OL,18,Fpatients to attend their appointments
OL,19,Funless they are told otherwise.
