OL,3,CSeveral people treated following
OL,4,Cchemical spill at Guy's Hospital
OL,6,FAround 150 people were evacuated from
OL,7,Fthe basement and ground floor of Guy's
OL,8,Fon Thursday morning.
OL,10,FFire and ambulance crews were called a
OL,11,Flittle before 9am following reports of
OL,12,Fa chemical incident.
OL,14,FThe chlorine gas is believed to have
OL,15,Fbeen produced by the mixing of
OL,16,Fchemicals inside a plant room.
OL,18,FEven small amounts of chlorine gas can
OL,19,Flead to irritation in the eyes, throat
OL,20,Fand lungs, while exposure to high
OL,21,Flevels can be fatal.
