OL,3,CSeveral people treated following
OL,4,Cchemical spill at Guy's Hospital
OL,6,FOne member of staff was injured as a
OL,7,Fresult of the incident, while several
OL,8,Fpeople ` who came to the aid of the
OL,9,Findividual ` have been treated for
OL,10,Fchlorine gas inhalation.
OL,12,FA London Ambulance Service
OL,13,Fspokesperson said: "We sent resources
OL,14,Fto the scene, including ambulance
OL,15,Fcrews, an incident response officer, a
OL,16,Fparamedic in a fast response car, an
OL,17,Femergency planning officer and
OL,18,Fparamedics from our hazardous area
OL,19,Fresponse team.
