OL,3,CSeveral people treated following
OL,4,Cchemical spill at Guy's Hospital
OL,6,F"We treated nine people at the scene.
OL,7,FWe took four patients to hospital and
OL,8,Fdischarged the other five patients at
OL,9,Fthe scene."
OL,11,FA statement from London Fire Brigade
OL,12,Fsaid: Firefighters have carried out a
OL,13,Fsweep of the area to check for no
OL,14,Felevated readings of chlorine gas.
OL,16,F"The building has also been
OL,17,Fventilated. Crews also supported with
OL,18,Fthe precautionary evacuation of the
OL,19,Fbasement and ground floors of the
OL,20,Fbuilding."
