OL,3,CSeveral people treated following
OL,4,Cchemical spill at Guy's Hospital
OL,6,FGuy's is a major elective centre with
OL,7,F400 beds, specialising in cancer,
OL,8,Fkidney, urology and dental care, as
OL,9,Fwell as ear, nose and throat and
OL,10,Forthopaedics.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Guy's and St
OL,13,FThomas's said on Thursday: "The London
OL,14,FFire Brigade attended a chemical
OL,15,Fincident in a non-patient area of
OL,16,FGuy's Hospital today.
OL,18,F"One staff member was injured and
OL,19,Fseveral people, who came to the aid of
OL,20,Fthe person, were treated for the
OL,21,Finhalation of chlorine gas.
